International Conference on Robotics and Automation Albuquerque, New Mexico - April 1997.</p>

<p>[2] QingXuan Jia et. al, "Analysis of Actuation for a Spherical Robot".2008 IEEE Conference on Robotics, Automation and Mechatronics. </p>

<p>[3] Erkan Kayacan et. al, "Modelling and control of a spherical rolling robot: a decoupled dynamics approach." Robotica: page 1 of 10.   Cambridge University Press 2011. (doi:10.1017/S0263574711000956) </p>

<p>[4] Wei-Hsi Chen et. al, "Design and implementation of a ball-driven omnidirectional spherical robot." Mechanism and Machine Theory 68 (2013) 35 48.</p>

